  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. To solve the equation, use the distributive property to multiply on the right-hand side of the equation which gives <span class=\"italic\">w</span><!--StartFragment--> &ndash;<!--EndFragment--> 10 = 2<span class=\"italic\">w </span>+ 10. Subtract <span class=\"italic\">w</span> from both sides of the equation, which gives &ndash;<!--EndFragment-->10 = <span class=\"italic\">w </span>+ 10. Finally, subtract 10 from both sides of the equation, which gives &ndash;<!--EndFragment-->20 = <span class=\"italic\">w.</span><p>Choices A and B are incorrect and may result from making sign errors. Choice C is incorrect and may result from incompletely distributing the 2 in the expression 2(<span class=\"italic\">w</span> + 5).</p></p>\n",
